\c 37
\s Josefa anotengeswa navakoma vake
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jakove akagara munyika youtorwa hwababa vake, munyika yeKenani.
\p
\v 2 Marudzi aJakove ndiwo: Josefa akange ana makore ane gumi namanomwe, akafudza makwai pamwechete navakoma vake; akange achiri mukomana pamwechete navanakomana vaBhiriha, navanakomana vaZiripa, vakadzi vababa vake; Josefa akasivaudzira kuna baba vavo.
\p
\v 3 Zvino Israeri akange achida Josefa kupfuura vana vake vose, nekuti aiva mwanakomana woutana hwake; akamuitira nguwo yakange yakareba ina maoko.
\v 4 Vakoma vake vakaona kuti baba vavo vanomuda kupfuura vakoma vake vose; vakamuvenga, vakasagona kutaura naye nomufaro.
\p
\v 5 Zvino Josefa akarota hope, akaudza vakoma vake, ipapo vakanyanya kumuvenga.
\v 6 Akati kwavari, Inzwaiwo hope dzangu dzandarota.
\v 7 Tarirai, takanga tichisunga zvisote mumunda, onei chisote changu chikasimuka, chikaramba chimire; ndikaona zvisote zvenyu zvichikomba changu, zvikakotama pamberi pechisote changu.
\p
\v 8 Vakoma vake vakati kwaari, Ko iwe uchabata ushe pamusoro pedu kanhi? Ko iwe uchava nesimba pamusoro pedu kanhi? Vakanyanya kumuvenga nokuda kokurota kwake nokwamashoko ake.
\p
\v 9 Akapamha kurotazve, akaudza vakoma vake, akati, Tarirai, ndarotazve dzimwe hope; ndakaona zuva, nomwedzi, nenyeredzi dzine gumi neimwe, dzichikotamira pamberi pangu.
\p
\v 10 Akaudza baba vake navakoma vake izvozvo; baba vake vakamutuka, vakati kwaari, Kurota kwako uku kwawarota kurota kunyi? Ini namai vako navakoma vako tichauya tikakotama pasi pamberi pako kanhi?
\v 11 Vakoma vake vakamugodora; asi baba vake vakachengeta shoko iro.
\v 12 Zvino vakoma vake vakanofudza makwai ababa vavo paShekemu.
\v 13 Israeri akati kuna Josefa, Vakoma vako havafudzi makwai paShekemu here? Uya ndikutumire kwavari. Iye akati, Ndiri pano hangu.
\p
\v 14 Akati kwaari, Zvino chienda undotarira kana vakoma vako vakafara, namakwai kana akafarawo; ugodzoka kuzondiudza. Naizvozvo akamutuma, ari pamupata weHebhuroni, akanosvika Shekemu.
\v 15 Zvino umwe murume akamuwana achidzungaira musango; murume akamubvunza, akati, Unotsvakeiko?
\p
\v 16 Iye akati, Ndinotsvaka vakoma vangu; dondiudza hako kwavanofudza makwai.
\p
\v 17 Murume akati, Vabva pano, nokuti ndakavanzwa vachiti, Ngatiende Dhotani. Josefa akatevera vakoma vake, akanovawana paDhotani.
\p
\v 18 Ivo vakamuona achiri kure; zvino asati asvika kwavari, vakarangana kuti vamuuraye.
\v 19 Vakataurirana, vachiti, Hoyo muroti uya wauya.
\v 20 Uyai zvino timuuraye, timukandire mune rimwe ramakomba aya, tigoti, Wadyiwa nechikara; tigoona kuti kurota kwake kuchazoitwa seiko.
\p
\v 21 Rubheni akazvinzwa, akamurwira mumaoko avo, akati, Ngatirege kumuuraya.
\v 22 Rubheni akati kwavari, Musadurura ropa; mukandirei mugomba iri riri musango, asi regai kutambanudza maoko enyu kwaari; kuti amurwire pamaoko avo, agomudzosera kuna baba vake.
\v 23 Zvino Josefa akati asvika kuvakoma vake, vakabvisira Josefa nguwo yake, nguwo iya yakange yakareba ina maoko, yaakanga akafuka;
\v 24 vakamutora, vakamukandira mugomba; gomba rakange risina chinhu, makange musina mvura.
\p
\v 25 Vakagara pasi, vakadya zvokudya; zvino vakasimudza meso avo, vakatarira, vakaona boka ravaIshimaeri vachifamba, vachibva Giriyadhi, makamera avo akatakura zvinhu zvinonhuhwira, nebarisami, nemura, vachindozviisa Egipita.
\v 26 Zvino Judha akati kuvana vababa vake, Tingawaneiko kana tikauraya munin'ina wedu tichivanza ropa rake?
\v 27 Uyai timutengese kuvaIshimaeri; maoko edu arege kuva kwaari; nekuti munun una wedu, nyama imwe nesu. Vana vababa vake vakamuteerera.
\v 28 Zvino vatengesi vavaMidhiani vakapfuurapo, vakakwidza Josefa vachimubudisa mugomba, vakatengesa Josefa kuvaIshimaeri namashekeri ana makumi maviri; ivo vakaisa Josefa Egipita.
\p
\v 29 Zvino Rubheni akadzokera kugomba, akawana Josefa asisimo mugomba; akabvarura nguwo dzake.
\v 30 Akadzokera kuvanin'ina vake, akati, Mwana haachipo; ini zvino ndichaendepiko?
\p
\v 31 Zvino vakatora nguwo yaJosefa, vakauraya nhongo yembudzi, vakanyika nguwo muropa;
\v 32 vakatumira nguwo iyo yakareba ina maoko kuna baba vavo, vakati, Tanonga chinhu ichi; fananidzai zvakanaka kana iri nguwo yomwanakomana wenyu, kana isati iri iyo.
\p
\v 33 Ivo vakafananidza vakati, Inguvo yomwanakomana wangu; wadyiwa nechikara; Josefa zvirokwazvo waparadzwa.
\v 34 Jakove akabvarura nguwo dzake, akasimira madhumbu pachiuno chake, akachema mwanakomana wake mazuva mazhinji.
\v 35 Vanakomana vake vose navakunda vake vose vakasimuka vakamunyaradza; asi akaramba kunyaradzwa, akati, Ndichaburukira kuguva kumwanakomana wangu, ndichichema. Baba vake vakamuwungudzira.
\p
\v 36 Zvino vaMidhiani vakanomutengesa Egipita kuna Potifari, muranda waFarao, mukuru wavarindi.
